data.description: Welcome to your dream smart/solar home! This immaculate 3 bedrms, 2.5 bathrms haven is a testament to design, elegance & comfort. Nestled in the gated Craig Ranch community offering parks & walking trails. This well maintained gem offers over 2100 square feet of pure luxury. Step into the breathtaking open floor plan with an expansive living room & dining area. The heart of this home is the chef's kitchen featuring an oversized quartz island, cherry wood cabinets, ample counter space & walk-in pantry. Enjoy the den/office space, loft & large laundry room for added convenience. The primary suite offers dual vanities & a large walk-in closet. Relax in the beautifully landscaped backyard. This home comes partially furnished. Easy access to all major freeways. Convenient shopping, dining, gaming, hospitals & live entertainment. Don't miss this opportunity to make this exquisite home your own. Schedule a viewing today & envision the wonderful memories you'll create in this stunning abode.
